OL,3,CHow a toddler was targeted by his own
OL,4,Cfamily in the weeks before his murder
OL,6,FLeading up to his death, Ethan was
OL,7,Fvulnerable, malnourished, severely
OL,8,Fdehydrated and covered in bruises.
OL,10,FDuring his short life, he lived in
OL,11,Fmultiple homes and at times had been
OL,12,Fprevented from seeing health and
OL,13,Fsocial workers. That's despite being
OL,14,Fplaced on the child protection
OL,15,Fregister when he moved into his
OL,16,Fgrandparents' home just one month
OL,17,Fbefore he died from a catastrophic
OL,18,Fbrain injury.
