OL,3,CHow a toddler was targeted by his own
OL,4,Cfamily in the weeks before his murder
OL,6,FHe collapsed in the living room of
OL,7,Ftheir home in Garden City, Flintshire,
OL,8,Fon August 14 2021. Only Michael and
OL,9,FKerry Ives were there. Only they know
OL,10,Fwhat really happened and why it took
OL,11,F18 minutes for a call to be made to
OL,12,Fparamedics.
