OL,3,CHow a toddler was targeted by his own
OL,4,Cfamily in the weeks before his murder
OL,6,FIt was suggested they delayed dialling
OL,7,F999 as they tried to get their story
OL,8,Fstraight. The prosecution said the
OL,9,Fpair entered a pact of silence,
OL,10,Fimmediately working as a team of two
OL,11,Fto conceal the reason Ethan had
OL,12,Fcollapsed. They both had something
OL,13,Fserious to hide. They were both
OL,14,Finvolved in causing his death. They
OL,15,Ftook a deliberate decision to lie and
OL,16,Fconceal the truth. This was a couple
OL,17,Fwho defended each other in court and
OL,18,Ftried to put the blame on their
OL,19,Fdaughter Shannon.
