OL,3,CHow a toddler was targeted by his own
OL,4,Cfamily in the weeks before his murder
OL,6,FHis limp body was carried out in the
OL,7,Farms of an emergency worker and he was
OL,8,Ftaken in an ambulance to the Countess
OL,9,Fof Chester Hospital. He would be
OL,10,Ftransferred to Alder Hey, a specialist
OL,11,Fchildren's hospital in Liverpool where
OL,12,Fhe would die on August 16.
OL,14,FThis case was unusual due to the
OL,15,Famount of CCTV and video footage
OL,16,Favailable to the prosecution.
