OL,3,CHow a toddler was targeted by his own
OL,4,Cfamily in the weeks before his murder
OL,6,FSurveillance cameras showed Michael
OL,7,FIves picking Ethan up from a
OL,8,Ftrampoline in the back garden and
OL,9,Fholding him aloft by one arm. The
OL,10,Fcourt heard how he was carried like a
OL,11,F"rag doll" or a "bag of rubbish." He
OL,12,Fwas also recorded gesturing with a
OL,13,Fclosed fist to one child, who then hit
OL,14,FEthan several times in the head.
OL,16,FAt times both Shannon and Kerry were
OL,17,Fin attendance. Neither stepped in to
OL,18,Fhelp or stop the cruelty.
