OL,3,CHow a toddler was targeted by his own
OL,4,Cfamily in the weeks before his murder
OL,6,FOther footage showed Michael Ives
OL,7,Fappearing to punch Ethan in the
OL,8,Fstomach as he put him in his car seat
OL,9,Fand mocking Ethan's unbalanced walk,
OL,10,Flaughing with Shannon as he imitated
OL,11,Fthe youngster. We now know his walk
OL,12,Fwas because of the head injuries he
OL,13,Fhad sustained and his severe
OL,14,Fdehydration.
OL,16,FHe was brought up in a home where he
OL,17,Fwas picked on and other children were
OL,18,Fencouraged to be mean to him.
