OL,3,CHow a toddler was targeted by his own
OL,4,Cfamily in the weeks before his murder
OL,6,FThe bruises found on Ethan's body were
OL,7,Fput down to him being clumsy and a
OL,8,Flittle boy "who walks into things".
OL,9,FHis grandmother Kerry said the toddler
OL,10,Fwas "accident prone".
OL,12,FHowever, the external injuries were
OL,13,Fdown to inflicted violence and the
OL,14,Ftoddler would have been in pain. His
OL,15,Fbrain injury was likened to one
OL,16,Fsomeone would endure from being in a
OL,17,Fhigh-speed collision.
