OL,3,CHow a toddler was targeted by his own
OL,4,Cfamily in the weeks before his murder
OL,6,FThere were times in his life that
OL,7,FEthan did not get the correct care and
OL,8,Fattention. At one point his mother
OL,9,FShannon had failed to register him
OL,10,Fwith a GP. She received warning
OL,11,Fletters from social services asking
OL,12,Fher to contact them.
OL,14,FHis mother and grandparents failed to
OL,15,Fget him medical attention after he
OL,16,Fcollapsed on 13 August - 24 hours
OL,17,Fbefore he collapsed again, never to
OL,18,Fregain consciousness, in the living
OL,19,Froom of Kingsley Road.
