OL,3,CHow a toddler was targeted by his own
OL,4,Cfamily in the weeks before his murder
OL,6,FFlintshire County Council's social
OL,7,Fservices team should have seen Ethan
OL,8,FIves Griffiths every 10 days after he
OL,9,Fwas placed on the child protection
OL,10,Fregister on July 6 2021.
OL,12,FHe was in the back garden on July 22
OL,13,Fby social worker Michael Cornish but
OL,14,Fthereafter Mr Cornish was stonewalled.
