OL,3,CHow a toddler was targeted by his own
OL,4,Cfamily in the weeks before his murder
OL,6,FIn 2021, the UK was still recovering
OL,7,Ffrom the pandemic. Due to restrictions
OL,8,Faround Covid and people isolating, Mr
OL,9,FCornish spoke to Ethan's mother
OL,10,FShannon Ives on the doorstep when he
OL,11,Fcalled on August 5. She said Ethan was
OL,12,Fsleeping and he was not seen that day.
OL,14,FOn August 12, two days before Ethan's
OL,15,Fcollapse, Mr Cornish returned with a
OL,16,Fhealth visitor but there was no answer
OL,17,Fat the address and a phone call was
OL,18,Falso unanswered.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/16
