OL,3,CHow a toddler was targeted by his own
OL,4,Cfamily in the weeks before his murder
OL,6,FMr Cornish went on leave but emailed
OL,7,Fhis manager to say Ethan needed to be
OL,8,Fseen.
OL,10,FEthan Ives-Griffiths was not seen on
OL,11,Fany CCTV footage which captured
OL,12,Fmovement in and out of the house for
OL,13,Fnearly a week between August 4 and
OL,14,FAugust 12. He would collapse in that
OL,15,Fhome, two days later.
OL,17,FA jury at Mold Crown Court convicted
OL,18,Fhis grandfather Michael Ives, 47, and
OL,19,Fgrandmother Kerry Ives, 46, of his
OL,20,Fmurder and of cruelty to a child under
OL,21,F16.
