OL,6,FEthan's mother Shannon Ives, 28, was
OL,7,Ffound guilty of causing or allowing
OL,8,Fhis death and of child cruelty.
OL,10,FA sentencing hearing for all three has
OL,11,Fbeen set for October 3.
